# MBKH Feature Architecture

- Follow strict flow: `View -> Controller -> UseCase -> Repository -> DataSource`.
- Organize code under `lib/features/<feature_name>/`.
- Keep responsive wrapper in `<feature>_view.dart` and concrete UIs in `presentation/`.
- Register routes in navigation files and dependencies in `lib/di.dart`.
